# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:35
translate spanish hwb_s30_e5772211:

    # "The glow from the half-opened skylight creeps in from above and shines down a strand of light onto the blanket. It divides the bed in two and slowly spreads across the room, casting off the morning shadows."
    "El resplandor del tragaluz entreabierto se cuela desde arriba y proyecta un haz de luz sobre la cobija. Divide la cama en dos y se extiende lentamente por la habitación, disipando las sombras de la mañana."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:37
translate spanish hwb_s30_2fe799c2:

    # "My palm is warm and sweaty. Moving my fingers reveals my hand is still interlocked with Marina’s."
    "Mi palma está caliente y sudorosa. Al mover los dedos, descubro que mi mano sigue entrelazada con la de Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:41
translate spanish hwb_s30_a9e0bb22:

    # "She never let go."
    "Nunca me soltó."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:43
translate spanish hwb_s30_151edb36:

    # "I turn over and face her. She’s still sleeping, curled on her side and laying on her arm. Just so she can keep holding my hand."
    "Me doy la vuelta y la miro. Sigue durmiendo, acurrucada de lado y apoyada sobre su brazo. Solo para poder seguir sosteniendo mi mano."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:45
translate spanish hwb_s30_26249aba:

    # "Soft and rhythmic, her breath brushes against my face."
    "Suave y rítmico, su aliento roza mi rostro."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:47
translate spanish hwb_s30_65503d13:

    # "If I could, I’d watch her for hours."
    "Si pudiera, la observaría durante horas."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:49
translate spanish hwb_s30_8790b235:

    # "Trying not to wake her, I unchain my fingers, wiggling them until the numbness sets in and pricks away at my sleeping hand."
    "Tratando de no despertarla, desenredo mis dedos, moviéndolos hasta que el entumecimiento se instala y punza mi mano dormida."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:51
translate spanish hwb_s30_56efec67:

    # "Marina’s nose wrinkles and the steady breathing stops."
    "La nariz de Marina se arruga y la respiración constante se detiene."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:53
translate spanish hwb_s30_98bbe0fd:

    # "Swallowing, her eyes flutter open and she smiles. The day’s first word slips out of her with a yawn."
    "Tragando saliva, sus ojos parpadean y se abren, y sonríe. La primera palabra del día se escapa de sus labios con un bostezo."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:55
translate spanish hwb_s30_a3db5978:

    # Marina "‘Morning."
    Marina "Доброе утро."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:57
translate spanish hwb_s30_dcdf6221:

    # Amber "Sorry, did I wake you up?"
    Amber "Прости, я тебя разбудила? "

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:59
translate spanish hwb_s30_a8320f62:

    # Marina "Mnm."
    Marina "М-м."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:61
translate spanish hwb_s30_5b3f5864:

    # "She snuggles in closer and takes a deep breath, keeping her deep, wide eyes on me."
    "Se acurruca más cerca y respira hondo, manteniendo sus ojos profundos y abiertos fijos en mí."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:63
translate spanish hwb_s30_36b30455:

    # Marina "You sleep okay?"
    Marina "Ты хорошо спала?"

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:65
translate spanish hwb_s30_3c0337a9:

    # "After the Fire Wave, Marina seemed unsure for a bit. But when I look at her now, none of that is there anymore."
    "Después de la Ola de Fuego, Marina parecía insegura por un momento. Pero cuando la miro ahora, ya no queda nada de eso."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:67
translate spanish hwb_s30_8c4c8e43:

    # "She’s completely trusting."
    "Confía completamente."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:69
translate spanish hwb_s30_3804b91e:

    # "It’s a little terrifying that I gained that trust so fast, especially since we pivoted around each other for so long."
    "Es un poco aterrador que haya ganado esa confianza tan rápido, especialmente después de haber girado una alrededor de la otra durante tanto tiempo."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:71
translate spanish hwb_s30_c53172b6:

    # "That kind of trust, that kind of responsibility—it’s a very special thing."
    "Ese tipo de confianza, ese tipo de responsabilidad, es algo muy especial."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:73
translate spanish hwb_s30_a8df0c8e:

    # "I had it with Gramps, and now Marina has given the same thing to me."
    "La tuve con el Abuelo, y ahora Marina me ha dado lo mismo."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:75
translate spanish hwb_s30_1e505a4a:

    # "From taking her to a gas station, finding treasure, and even fending off weirdos. She’s put her trust in me to be responsible for all of it."
    "Desde llevarla a una gasolinera, encontrar tesoros, hasta ahuyentar a los raritos. Ha puesto su confianza en mí para que me encargue de todo."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:77
translate spanish hwb_s30_9f75f011:

    # "Sometimes I wonder if I deserve it."
    "A veces me pregunto si lo merezco."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:79
translate spanish hwb_s30_6c730138:

    # "Sometimes I have moments where I know I don’t."
    "A veces tengo momentos en los que sé que no."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:81
translate spanish hwb_s30_8a4c16e2:

    # "Like when I can’t find some lousy treasure. Like when I’m not around to help her out of a jam. Like when nothing I do can save someone, no matter how hard I try."
    "Como cuando no puedo encontrar un tesoro de mala muerte. Como cuando no estoy cerca para sacarla de un apuro. Como cuando nada de lo que hago puede salvar a alguien, por más que lo intente."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:83
translate spanish hwb_s30_3ac8c129:

    # "Like when I just can’t function."
    "Como cuando simplemente no puedo funcionar."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:85
translate spanish hwb_s30_c3120319:

    # "Like last night."
    "Como anoche."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:87
translate spanish hwb_s30_7e359ea9:

    # "Marina picks up on my silence. Her expression fades from trust to concern."
    "Marina capta mi silencio. Su expresión pasa de confianza a preocupación."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:89
translate spanish hwb_s30_3a16d28e:

    # Marina "Something wrong?"
    Marina "Что-то не так?"

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:91
translate spanish hwb_s30_88045c4d:

    # Amber "Nah, it’s all good. Slept fine."
    Amber "Нет, все в порядке. Спала хорошо."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:93
translate spanish hwb_s30_e1094eee:

    # "I lean over to kiss her forehead, but pull back halfway."
    "Me inclino para besarle la frente, pero me detengo a medio camino."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:95
translate spanish hwb_s30_47781d29:

    # "Ripping off the blanket, I leap out of bed and stretch."
    "Arrancando la cobija, salto de la cama y me estiro."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:97
translate spanish hwb_s30_6deac0ba:

    # "Marina turns a crimson red and ‘eeps,’ throwing the covers over herself as our clothes from last night lie in heaps across the room."
    "Marina se pone roja como un tomate y hace un \"eep\", tirando las sábanas sobre sí misma mientras nuestra ropa de anoche yace en montones por toda la habitación."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:107
translate spanish hwb_s30_da36908f:

    # "I dig through the cupboard and toss her a change of clothes before slipping into my own and beginning our morning routine."
    "Busco en el armario y le lanzo un cambio de ropa antes de ponerme la mía y comenzar nuestra rutina matutina."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:109
translate spanish hwb_s30_41ad004a:

    # Amber "We got a big day ahead of us. Assuming traffic isn’t crap, we should be in Palm Springs by late noon."
    Amber "Впереди у нас трудный день. Если пробок не будет, то к концу дня мы должны быть уже в Палм Спрингс."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:111
translate spanish hwb_s30_d3699fdf:

    # "She peeks out from the blanket and grabs her clothes."
    "Ella asoma la cabeza por debajo de la cobija y agarra su ropa."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:113
translate spanish hwb_s30_14373672:

    # Marina "And then the festival?"
    Marina "И потом фестиваль?"

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:115
translate spanish hwb_s30_c47faa77:

    # Amber "Almost. We’ll have about a day to kill."
    Amber "Почти. У нас еще будет один день в запасе."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:117
translate spanish hwb_s30_256551c8:

    # "I run the coffee maker and head to the bathroom to start brushing my teeth."
    "Enciendo la cafetera y voy al baño a empezar a cepillarme los dientes."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:119
translate spanish hwb_s30_deed52b8:

    # "Behind me, Marina is changing into her clothes. I can clearly see her in the mirror, but after last night I’m not sure it matters anymore if I ‘accidentally’ catch a glimpse of her."
    "Detrás de mí, Marina se está cambiando. Puedo verla claramente en el espejo, pero después de anoche ya no estoy segura de que importe si \"accidentalmente\" le echo un vistazo."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:129
translate spanish hwb_s30_1d57c5a0:

    # Marina "So do you know what bands you’d like to see yet?"
    Marina "Ты уже решила, какие группы хотела бы увидеть?"

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:131
translate spanish hwb_s30_a4bfd112:

    # "My voice is garbled, muffled by the toothbrush stuffed in the corner of my mouth."
    "Mi voz sale distorsionada, amortiguada por el cepillo de dientes metido en la comisura de mi boca."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:136
translate spanish hwb_s30_801b90aa:

    # Amber "Kinda. I have a few ideas."
    Amber "Типа того. Есть пара идей."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:138
translate spanish hwb_s30_2ad9e997:

    # "{i}Spit.{/i}"
    "{i}Escupe.{/i}"

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:140
translate spanish hwb_s30_f8be4547:

    # "Most of which are just bands me and Gramps liked."
    "La mayoría son solo bandas que a mí y al Abuelo nos gustaban."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:144
translate spanish hwb_s30_8f0e9bda:

    # Amber "We should look at the lineup later. See if there aren’t a few bands you might wanna check out."
    Amber "Нужно глянуть список выступающих. Может там будут группы, которые тебе тоже захочется послушать."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:146
translate spanish hwb_s30_3429f9a8:

    # "Finished changing, she scoots in behind me, directing our eyes to the mirror as she rests her head on my shoulder."
    "Terminando de cambiarse, se desliza detrás de mí, dirigiendo nuestras miradas al espejo mientras apoya la cabeza en mi hombro."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:155
translate spanish hwb_s30_dc090c85:

    # Marina "Mmm. It’s fine. I’ll watch whoever you wanna watch, Amber."
    Marina "Ммм. Все нормально. Я буду слушать то же, что ты захочешь послушать, Эмбер."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:159
translate spanish hwb_s30_cc1ea62c:

    # "I watch the mirror as my face goes blank."
    "Miro el espejo mientras mi cara se queda en blanco."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:161
translate spanish hwb_s30_831cecae:

    # "Marina nuzzles against my cheek, bringing with her an aching burden that presses down on my entire being."
    "Marina se acurruca contra mi mejilla, trayendo consigo una carga dolorosa que presiona todo mi ser."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:165
translate spanish hwb_s30_3f0fb252:

    # "Why does she believe in me so much? Even when I’m such a wreck."
    "¿Por qué cree tanto en mí? Incluso cuando soy un desastre."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:167
translate spanish hwb_s30_67234d85:

    # "The coffee maker beeps, saving me from being crushed by my own thoughts."
    "La cafetera emite un pitido, salvándome de ser aplastada por mis propios pensamientos."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:173
translate spanish hwb_s30_26fcd79f:

    # "I rip myself away from her."
    "Me arranco de ella."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:175
translate spanish hwb_s30_387d8368:

    # Amber "Anyway, get ready. We’re gonna hit the road as soon as you’re done."
    Amber "В любом случае, собирайся. Мы выезжаем сразу, как будешь готова."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:179
translate spanish hwb_s30_eafcab10:

    # "I rush to the sink. Steam rises out of the cup as my shaky hand pours the coffee, splattering most of it on the counter."
    "Corro al fregadero. El vapor sube de la taza mientras mi mano temblorosa sirve el café, salpicando la mayor parte en la encimera."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:183
translate spanish hwb_s30_ab1a76ea:

    # "Steadying myself doesn’t work. My body won’t listen. The burning coffee splashes on my skin as I wrench it to my mouth. It scalds my tongue and blisters down my throat. The pain sizzles all the way to my stomach."
    "Calmarme no funciona. Mi cuerpo no obedece. El café hirviendo me salpica la piel mientras lo llevo a mi boca. Me quema la lengua y ampolla la garganta. El dolor chisporrotea hasta el estómago."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:187
translate spanish hwb_s30_bc2786c2:

    # "I gasp out a short scream, but quickly muffle it with my hand. With tears forming, I turn and make sure Marina didn’t hear it over the running water."
    "Dejo escapar un grito corto, pero rápidamente lo amortiguo con la mano. Con lágrimas formándose, me giro y me aseguro de que Marina no lo haya oído por encima del agua corriendo."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:191
translate spanish hwb_s30_e06ed689:

    # "Once I’m sure, I wipe my eyes. After several sharp breaths, I pour myself another cup."
    "Una vez que estoy segura, me seco los ojos. Después de varias respiraciones profundas, me sirvo otra taza."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:222
translate spanish hwb_s30_8c2aff5b:

    # "I drag myself to the driver’s seat and slam my cup in the holder, then plant my head on the steering wheel. It honks."
    "Me arrastro hasta el asiento del conductor y golpeo mi taza en el portavasos, luego apoyo la cabeza en el volante. Suena el claxon."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:224
translate spanish hwb_s30_8165013c:

    # "The handles from the bathroom squeak and the sound of water is reduced to a drip."
    "Las manijas del baño chirrían y el sonido del agua se reduce a un goteo."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:231
translate spanish hwb_s30_79c9191e:

    # "A few moments later, Marina trots down the motorhome and hops into her seat."
    "Unos momentos después, Marina trota por la casa rodante y salta a su asiento."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:236
translate spanish hwb_s30_da395aab:

    # "I jerk up my head."
    "Levanto la cabeza de golpe."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:238
translate spanish hwb_s30_7502f73e:

    # Amber "All set?"
    Amber "Готова?"

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:242
translate spanish hwb_s30_7de595db:

    # Marina "Yup!"
    Marina "Ага!"

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:244
translate spanish hwb_s30_db1915f0:

    # Marina "But…"
    Marina "Только..."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:248
translate spanish hwb_s30_5d8a9ca9:

    # Marina "Are you sure nothing’s wrong?"
    Marina "Ты уверена, что все в порядке?"

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:252
translate spanish hwb_s30_552ebb0e:

    # "Forcing a smile, I turn the key and put the RV into drive."
    "Forzando una sonrisa, giro la llave y pongo la casa rodante en marcha."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:256
translate spanish hwb_s30_8bfc4905:

    # Amber "Don’t worry, everything’s fine. Just a little tired."
    Amber "Не переживай, все в порядке. Просто немного устала."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:260
translate spanish hwb_s30_78cc4144:

    # "Marina studies me for a few seconds, then shrugs and looks out the window, happily staring at the giant thermometer outside."
    "Marina me estudia por unos segundos, luego se encoge de hombros y mira por la ventana, observando feliz el termómetro gigante de afuera."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:264
translate spanish hwb_s30_d43e85f0:

    # "I pick up Gramps’ favorite tape and put it in the player, still staring at Marina."
    "Tomo el casete favorito del abuelo y lo pongo en el reproductor, todavía mirando a Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:268
translate spanish hwb_s30_d2cbfd72:

    # "Frowning, I catch a glimpse of myself in the rear view mirror."
    "Frunciendo el ceño, me veo de reojo en el espejo retrovisor."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:270
translate spanish hwb_s30_7137f12c:

    # "Please don’t hurt her. Please."
    "Por favor, no le hagas daño. Por favor."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:292
translate spanish hwb_s30_82aac332:

    # Marina "Oooh and it says here that there are giant dinosaurs statues just up ahead!"
    Marina "Огоо, тут написано, что впереди мы увидим огромные статуи динозавров!"

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:296
translate spanish hwb_s30_e76f551c:

    # Amber "Oh that’s great."
    Amber "О, это здорово."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:300
translate spanish hwb_s30_7f39fe3f:

    # "Everything she’s been saying for the past few hours has been zooming right past me."
    "Todo lo que ha estado diciendo durante las últimas horas me ha pasado de largo."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:302
translate spanish hwb_s30_2f64f793:

    # "It’s not that I don’t understand it. I’ve read that guidebook she’s been pointing to about a thousand times as a kid. But it’s all being drowned out by the music and my constant thinking."
    "No es que no lo entienda. He leído esa guía a la que señala como mil veces cuando era niña. Pero todo se ahoga entre la música y mis pensamientos constantes."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:304
translate spanish hwb_s30_86008e70:

    # "The drive hasn’t done much to soothe the budding anxiety inside me."
    "El viaje no ha hecho mucho por calmar la incipiente ansiedad dentro de mí."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:306
translate spanish hwb_s30_b6131370:

    # "In fact, I’d say it’s just made it worse."
    "De hecho, diría que solo la ha empeorado."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:308
translate spanish hwb_s30_11af87bd:

    # "After four states worth of desert and endless stretches of road, it’s maddening to see it all get mauled over by overpasses and the slowest, most painful and rage-inducing traffic I’ve ever seen."
    "Después de cuatro estados de desierto y tramos interminables de carretera, es exasperante verlo todo destrozado por pasos elevados y el tráfico más lento, doloroso y que provoca ira que he visto jamás."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:310
translate spanish hwb_s30_e355866d:

    # "With nothing but Gramps’ tape to keep me grounded, it’s been a battle not to go mental."
    "Con nada más que el casete del abuelo para mantenerme centrada, ha sido una lucha no volverme loca."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:312
translate spanish hwb_s30_f956c297:

    # "My mind keeps wandering back to Marina. How we’re together. What exactly that means. Her trust. My responsibility."
    "Mi mente no deja de divagar hacia Marina. Cómo estamos juntas. Qué significa exactamente eso. Su confianza. Mi responsabilidad."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:314
translate spanish hwb_s30_3f839062:

    # "And the more I think about it, the more I th—"
    "Y cuanto más pienso en ello, más—"

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:320
translate spanish hwb_s30_93c72a5a:

    # Marina "Oh wow! Amber, look how white the sand is, it’s like snow!"
    Marina "Ух ты! Эмбер, смотри, какой белый песок! Прямо как снег!"

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:326
translate spanish hwb_s30_43bffd17:

    # "Her observations haven’t been helping either."
    "Sus observaciones tampoco han ayudado."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:328
translate spanish hwb_s30_8fba67a6:

    # "Whenever I’m about to make a breakthrough or convince myself I’m just thinking too hard, she pipes in and suddenly I feel like I’m right back to where I started in Colorado."
    "Cada vez que estoy a punto de tener una revelación o convencerme de que solo estoy pensando demasiado, ella interviene y de repente siento que estoy justo donde empecé en Colorado."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:330
translate spanish hwb_s30_1aa0af83:

    # "At least I can take solace in the scenery going back to something more familiar as we get closer to Palm Springs."
    "Al menos puedo consolarme con que el paisaje vuelve a ser más familiar a medida que nos acercamos a Palm Springs."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:332
translate spanish hwb_s30_81a1e029:

    # "Like Marina said, the sand is a lot whiter, and looks almost as soft as cotton. It fades into fields of rocks and dry plants, trailing into expansive mountain ranges. All this. Just off the side of the road."
    "Como dijo Marina, la arena es mucho más blanca y se ve casi tan suave como el algodón. Se desvanece en campos de rocas y plantas secas, que se extienden hacia cadenas montañosas expansivas. Todo esto. Justo al lado de la carretera."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:334
translate spanish hwb_s30_372d96b8:

    # "It feels like the kind of desert people wander around and go crazy in."
    "Se siente como el tipo de desierto donde la gente deambula y se vuelve loca."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:336
translate spanish hwb_s30_c4305aa9:

    # "Something I can very much sympathize with."
    "Algo con lo que puedo sentirme muy identificada."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:338
translate spanish hwb_s30_f0b8781f:

    # "After all, wandering around in a desert and going crazy is how I met Marina."
    "Después de todo, deambular por un desierto y volverme loca fue como conocí a Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:340
translate spanish hwb_s30_edb844ee:

    # "I think that’s where the seeds of trust and responsibility were sewn."
    "Creo que ahí fue donde se sembraron las semillas de la confianza y la responsabilidad."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:342
translate spanish hwb_s30_80b05747:

    # "At least I like to think that’s why she trusts me—because I helped her."
    "Al menos me gusta pensar que por eso confía en mí, porque la ayudé."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:344
translate spanish hwb_s30_a9b57f42:

    # "And it’s through the next few weeks that that trust was built upon, cultivating in something maybe even greater than that."
    "Y es durante las siguientes semanas que esa confianza se fue construyendo, cultivando algo quizás incluso más grande que eso."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:346
translate spanish hwb_s30_6c17ddfb:

    # "Marina became important to me, someone I had to protect."
    "Marina se volvió importante para mí, alguien a quien debía proteger."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:352
translate spanish hwb_s30_b4bfd784:

    # Marina "Woah. Look at all the windmills!"
    Marina "Вау, посмотри на все эти ветряки!"

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:356
translate spanish hwb_s30_03739bb9:

    # "I clench down on the steering wheel."
    "Aprieto el volante."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:358
translate spanish hwb_s30_0f5eb572:

    # "By doing what we did last night, did I betray that sense of ‘greater than trust?’"
    "Al hacer lo que hicimos anoche, ¿traicioné ese sentido de \"más que confianza\"?"

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:360
translate spanish hwb_s30_546ca002:

    # "She saw me crying. She comforted me. I made a move, and…"
    "Me vio llorando. Me consoló. Yo di el primer paso, y..."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:364
translate spanish hwb_s30_eacca17b:

    # "Oh god."
    "Ay, Dios."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:366
translate spanish hwb_s30_7ca4d986:

    # "The realization is like a punch to the gut. I want to swerve off to the side of the road and hurl my guts out."
    "La revelación es como un puñetazo en el estómago. Quiero desviarme al costado de la carretera y vomitar hasta quedarme vacía."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:368
translate spanish hwb_s30_9dde3d40:

    # "I used her. I {i}used{/i} Marina."
    "Me aproveché de ella. {i}Usé{/i} a Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:372
translate spanish hwb_s30_e1bf6a3a:

    # Marina "Amber, loooook."
    Marina "Эмбер, смотриииии."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:376
translate spanish hwb_s30_46c5b75c:

    # "She tugs on my sleeve and points out the window."
    "Ella tira de mi manga y señala por la ventana."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:378
translate spanish hwb_s30_6dd2433e:

    # "As far as I can see into the hazy distance, an army of windmills line the sand and stretch all the way to the hilltops. Their wings spin down in unison, cycling with the steady wind."
    "Hasta donde alcanzo a ver en la distancia brumosa, un ejército de molinos de viento bordean la arena y se extienden hasta las cimas de las colinas. Sus aspas giran al unísono, ciclando con el viento constante."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:380
translate spanish hwb_s30_7a2386e3:

    # "It’s enough to snap me out of it, at least for a few seconds. But once the initial novelty wears off, I’m right back to where I’ve been for hours."
    "Es suficiente para sacarme de eso, al menos por unos segundos. Pero una vez que la novedad inicial se desvanece, vuelvo justo a donde he estado durante horas."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:384
translate spanish hwb_s30_7c2c50ea:

    # Marina "I’ve never seen so many…"
    Marina "Я никогда не видела так много..."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:386
translate spanish hwb_s30_6c8ed98a:

    # "Marina sounds completely blown away, enchanted even. It’s cute, but I need to think this through. {i}Really{/i} think this through."
    "Marina suena completamente impresionada, incluso encantada. Es lindo, pero necesito pensar esto con claridad. {i}De verdad{/i} pensar esto con claridad."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:394
translate spanish hwb_s30_6e3e7b92:

    # Amber "Hey, uh, do you think we could actually be quiet for a little while?"
    Amber "Эй, эм, может нам немного помолчать какое-то время?"

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:398
translate spanish hwb_s30_401f04ed:

    # Marina "Oh sure, that’s fine."
    Marina "Ок, ладно, без проблем."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:400
translate spanish hwb_s30_1131e1bc:

    # Amber "Thanks."
    Amber "Спасибо."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:406
translate spanish hwb_s30_5771c457:

    # "She goes back to looking out the window, swaying to the music."
    "Ella vuelve a mirar por la ventana, meciéndose al ritmo de la música."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:408
translate spanish hwb_s30_2aab741f:

    # "So pure. Innocent."
    "Tan pura. Inocente."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:410
translate spanish hwb_s30_4af2b0b2:

    # "And I took advantage of that."
    "Y yo me aproveché de eso."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:412
translate spanish hwb_s30_4ea45cea:

    # "Is that all I’ve been doing this entire time? Using her to make myself feel better?"
    "¿Es todo lo que he estado haciendo todo este tiempo? ¿Usarla para sentirme mejor?"

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:414
translate spanish hwb_s30_92f2a6de:

    # "I don’t even want to consider it, but it adds up."
    "Ni siquiera quiero considerarlo, pero todo tiene sentido."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:416
translate spanish hwb_s30_9f8ab7ce:

    # "I was lonely, didn’t have anyone else. Saw a cute girl, picked her up and consistently used her to curb that, all while telling myself that I was just helping and protecting her."
    "Estaba sola, no tenía a nadie más. Vi a una chica linda, la recogí y la usé constantemente para aliviar eso, todo mientras me decía a mí misma que solo la estaba ayudando y protegiendo."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:418
translate spanish hwb_s30_0d847095:

    # "And then I convinced myself of more, hoping to forget about the most important person in the world to me."
    "Y luego me convencí de algo más, esperando olvidar a la persona más importante del mundo para mí."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:424
translate spanish hwb_s30_d63f813a:

    # "The tape clicks to a stop, jolting me back to reality."
    "El casete hace clic al detenerse, sacudiéndome de vuelta a la realidad."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:428
translate spanish hwb_s30_8ca59e09:

    # "I eject it and flip it around, fumbling with the tape as I shove it back into the player and press play."
    "Lo expulso y le doy la vuelta, manoseando la cinta mientras la meto de nuevo en el reproductor y presiono play."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:430
translate spanish hwb_s30_be74fd05:

    # "It starts off the same as always. The same static. The same first note—everything."
    "Empieza igual que siempre. La misma estática. La misma primera nota, todo."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:434
translate spanish hwb_s30_0eb826ed:

    # "But soon, the audio starts to slip, like someone is sliding on the tape. The music jarbles into something distorted and ugly, speeding up, slowing down, and going backwards all at once."
    "Pero pronto, el audio comienza a distorsionarse, como si alguien estuviera deslizando la cinta. La música se vuelve algo distorsionado y feo, acelerándose, desacelerándose y yendo hacia atrás todo a la vez."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:438
translate spanish hwb_s30_029b4d09:

    # "I frantically push the eject button over and over, but it's too late. The deck spits out the tape, a string of tattered ribbon tangled around it."
    "Presiono frenéticamente el botón de expulsión una y otra vez, pero es demasiado tarde. El reproductor escupe el casete, con un hilo de cinta hecha jirones enredado a su alrededor."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:440
translate spanish hwb_s30_6ef70f9e:

    # "Marina is too captivated by something outside to notice what happened, but I feel all of it."
    "Marina está demasiado cautivada por algo afuera como para notar lo que pasó, pero yo lo siento todo."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:442
translate spanish hwb_s30_90a3fcb9:

    # "Tears start to swell up deep inside me, but it just morphs into fury."
    "Las lágrimas empiezan a brotar en lo profundo de mí, pero solo se transforman en furia."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:446
translate spanish hwb_s30_ed19aaa7:

    # Marina "Check it out! That mountain still has snow—"
    Marina "Гляди! На горе еще снег лежит-"

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:452
translate spanish hwb_s30_273e6821:

    # Amber "{size=+10}GODDAMMIT SHUT UP!{/size}" with hpunch
    Amber "{size=+10}ЧЕРТ ТЕБЯ ДЕРИ, ПОМОЛЧИ!{/size}" with hpunch

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:465
translate spanish hwb_s30_bb4b841d:

    # "As if the universe were conspiring against me, a deafening explosion blasts in front of us." with hpunch
    "Напротив нас раздался оглушительный взрыв. Черт, как будто вся вселенная ополчилась сегодня против меня." with hpunch

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:467
translate spanish hwb_s30_37c325c6:

    # "Tremors shake the motorhome. We bounce in our seats as I grip the wheel and pound on the brakes, swerving out of traffic."
    "Los temblores sacuden la casa rodante. Brincamos en nuestros asientos mientras agarro el volante y piso el freno, esquivando el tráfico."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:469
translate spanish hwb_s30_90f53703:

    # "Our hearts almost collide. Gasping for air, Marina turns to me for answers."
    "Nuestros corazones casi chocan. Jadeando por aire, Marina se gira hacia mí buscando respuestas."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:473
translate spanish hwb_s30_85ceedc2:

    # Amber "Dammit! Not now!"
    Amber "Черт подери! Только не сейчас!"

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:475
translate spanish hwb_s30_06d08fd8:

    # "I tear off my seatbelt and rush outside. Smoke rises from the engine, tearing into my lungs as I open the hood."
    "Me arranco el cinturón de seguridad y salgo corriendo. El humo sale del motor, desgarrándome los pulmones cuando abro el capó."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:508
translate spanish hwb_s30_fce6e6f7:

    # Amber "Shit!"
    Amber "Дерьмо!"

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:518
translate spanish hwb_s30_a0828e66:

    # "Marina runs to my side, waving away the smoke. Her jaw drops."
    "Marina corre a mi lado, apartando el humo con la mano. Se queda boquiabierta."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:520
translate spanish hwb_s30_0e22893e:

    # Marina "Oh my god, what happened?"
    Marina "О господи, что случилось?"

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:525
translate spanish hwb_s30_1b624533:

    # Amber "What do you think happened? The engine blew!"
    Amber "А ты что думаешь, случилось? Движок сдох!"

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:533
translate spanish hwb_s30_b1977ec8:

    # "I punt the bumper. It leaves a small dent, like my numb foot is made of steel."
    "Pateo el parachoques. Deja una pequeña abolladura, como si mi pie entumecido fuera de acero."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:535
translate spanish hwb_s30_060b5dd7:

    # Marina "Wh-What? But how?"
    Marina "Чт-Что? Но как?"

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:539
translate spanish hwb_s30_1ea29826:

    # Amber "How the hell would I know?"
    Amber "Откуда я, блин, знаю?"

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:545
translate spanish hwb_s30_9b1bc5c2:

    # "She flinches back, but manages to put on a hopeful smile."
    "Ella retrocede sobresaltada, pero logra esbozar una sonrisa esperanzadora."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:549
translate spanish hwb_s30_75b0f927:

    # Marina "We have some tools, maybe we can fix it!"
    Marina "У нас есть какие-то инструменты, может мы сможем его починить!"

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:555
translate spanish hwb_s30_c1d748e4:

    # "Laughing, I lean in and scoff in her face."
    "Riendo, me inclino y resoplo en su cara."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:557
translate spanish hwb_s30_fe6bb1ab:

    # Amber "Oh, you know how to fix the engine, Marina?"
    Amber "Охх, а ты, видимо, умеешь чинить двигатели, Марина?"

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:559
translate spanish hwb_s30_00903c34:

    # Marina "No, but I thought maybe you could..."
    Marina "Нет, но я думала, может, ты умеешь..."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:562
translate spanish hwb_s30_c6503201:

    # Amber "Do I look like a mechanic to you?"
    Amber "Я что, похожа на механика?"

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:566
translate spanish hwb_s30_fc53fecd:

    # "Marina wraps herself in the security of her arms and looks to the windmills, their wings casting thick, brief shadows over us."
    "Marina se envuelve en la seguridad de sus brazos y mira hacia los molinos de viento, cuyas aspas proyectan sombras gruesas y fugaces sobre nosotras."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:568
translate spanish hwb_s30_1d880139:

    # Marina "I just thought…"
    Marina "Я просто подумала..."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:570
translate spanish hwb_s30_fca770a9:

    # Amber "You {i}thought?{/i} The last time you {i}thought,{/i} you ended up broken down on the side of the road."
    Amber "Ты {i}подумала?{i} В последний раз, когда ты {i}подумала{i}, ты осталась одна на обочине со сломанной машиной."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:572
translate spanish hwb_s30_210c24c1:

    # Amber "So maybe it would be better for both of us if you continued not to {i}think.{/i}"
    Amber "Так что может для нас обеих будет лучше тебе вообще не {i}думать{i}."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:574
translate spanish hwb_s30_5318a060:

    # "She can hardly look at me. Her voice lowers to a fragile whisper, crackling as she speaks."
    "Apenas puede mirarme. Su voz baja a un susurro frágil, quebradizo mientras habla."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:578
translate spanish hwb_s30_eab4f687:

    # Marina "I just wanted to help."
    Marina "Я просто хотела помочь."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:580
translate spanish hwb_s30_bbbf0523:

    # Amber "Unless you can magically pull a phone out of your ass and call a tow truck, then you can’t."
    Amber "Единственно​​е, чем ты можешь помочь, это проделать невероятный фокус и вытащить телефон из своей задницы и вызвать эвакуатор."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:582
translate spanish hwb_s30_734ad1bd:

    # Amber "And even if you could, you would probably just let it get stolen."
    Amber "И даже если бы ты это сделала, трейлер наверняка бы угнали."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:586
translate spanish hwb_s30_77d65967:

    # "No response."
    "Sin respuesta."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:590
translate spanish hwb_s30_68fe0ec0:

    # Amber "You wanna make yourself useful? Go back into the RV."
    Amber "Хочешь хоть чем-нибудь помочь? Иди обратно в трейлер."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:596
translate spanish hwb_s30_3e42f5c3:

    # "Marina keeps her eyes to the ground. Without saying another word, she slinks back to her seat."
    "Marina mantiene la mirada en el suelo. Sin decir una palabra más, se escabulle de vuelta a su asiento."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:603
translate spanish hwb_s30_5da395f1:

    # "I sigh and space myself out in front of the motorhome, waving my hands back and forth as cars speed by, ignoring my signal."
    "Suspiro y me coloco frente a la casa rodante, moviendo las manos de un lado a otro mientras los autos pasan veloces, ignorando mi señal."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:605
translate spanish hwb_s30_4c73a87c:

    # "Even I can’t follow my own stupid advice."
    "Ni siquiera yo puedo seguir mi propio estúpido consejo."

# game/script/hwb_s30.rpy:292
translate spanish hwb_s30_a883ffd7:

    # Marina "Oooh and it says here that there are giant dinosaur statues just up ahead!"
    Marina "Огоо, тут написано, что впереди мы увидим огромные статуи динозавров!"

